text: Mia Musa Hossain is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Khulna-2. ==Career== Hossain was elected to parliament from Khulna-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mia Musa Hossain
